In <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">April</ENAMEX> , when many of them bought their CDs , <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">six - month</ENAMEX> certificates were yielding <ENAMEX TYPE="PERCENT">more than 9 %</ENAMEX> ; investors willing to look could find double - digit yields at some banks and thrifts .
